      "text": "• Commit initial\n  FastAPI + SQLModel + SQLite\n• 10 tables, 80+ versions\n• Architecture autoportante\n  (fonctionne sans JIRA)\n• Plugin JIRA optionnel\n  (sync proxy /jira/*)\n• Config PM2 + .env.example\n• Dashboard, Sprint, Kanban,\n  PI Planning, Roadmap, Health,\n  Retro, Support, ROAM, Agenda",
